### Status da API
GET http://127.0.0.1:4000/

### Listar usuários
GET http://127.0.0.1:4000/users

### Criar usuário
POST http://127.0.0.1:4000/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "_name": "Lucas",
  "_email": "lucas.escouto@saipos.com",
  "_password": "teste.teste7777"
}

### Buscar usuário por ID
GET http://127.0.0.1:4000/users/ieyGR8uUXolpB6pe
### Atualizar usuário por ID
PUT http://127.0.0.1:4000/users/ieyGR8uUXolpB6pe
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "_name": "Lucas Atualizado",
  "_email": "lucas.escouto@saipos.com",
  "_password": "alteração.teste"
}

### Remover usuário por ID
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:4000/users/IsmsWSQj3v3coa1g
